{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HYLXQe9mo4WTbd1SwC3L7M","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All files have been successfully read. Here are the contents:\n\n## 1. Title Extractor Implementation\n**File:** `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`\n\nThis is a comprehensive TypeScript module for extracting recipe titles from OCR text using both heuristic and semantic (embedding-based) approaches. It contains:\n\n- Pattern matching for measurement units, metadata patterns, and section labels (supporting both English and Polish)\n- Functions to filter out noise: `isLikelyGarbled()`, `looksLikeIngredient()`, `startsWithNumber()`\n- A candidate building system that merges consecutive lines and filters based on hard rules\n- An embedding-based scoring system that:\n  - Compares candidates against three reference embeddings (title, header, noise)\n  - Applies bonuses for ALL_CAPS text and structural headings\n  - Detects bilingual pages and suppresses translations\n  - Handles multi-recipe pages\n  - Deduplicates candidates by substring matching\n- Falls back to a simpler heuristic-only method for cases without embedding support\n\n---\n\n## 2. Test Results\n**File:** `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/18-1d256ae/results.txt`\n\nA list of 203 recipe titles with pass/fail indicators. From the sampled files you requested:\n- **Passing (yes):** Barszcz Czysty, Beef Bourguignon, Beet and Orange Salad, Bigos, Blueberry Cheesecake, Bruschetta, many others\n- **Failing (no):** Barszcz, Beef Stew, Beet Salad, Berry Jam, Bigos Myśliwski, Bigos z Wdzonych Kielbas, Blackberry Cobbler, Brownies, Buki Mleczne, Chocolate Brownies + Fudgy Chocolate Brownies, Chocolate Hazelnut Spread, Chocolate Lava Cake, Coleslaw, Crème Brûlée, Gęsina z Jabłkami, HERB BAKED SALMON + DILL SAUCE VARIATION, Kluski Śląskie, Konfitury ze Liwek, Krem Grzybowy ze Śmietaną, Lamb Stew, Lem