{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MyjqvPPa9ozuPwMG23Hu3m","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→SEZON: WIOSNA\n     2→\n     3→Beet Salad\n     4→\n     5→This dish represents the very best of home cooking traditions. Serve warm to fully appreciate its complex flavors.\n     6→Tradycyjny sposób przygotowania, który gwarantuje doskonały smak i doskonałą teksturę.\n     7→Originating from ancient culinary traditions, this preparation method ensures maximum flavor extraction and nutritional retention.\n     8→This classic dish brings warmth and comfort to any table. Perfect for family gatherings, it's been passed down through generations with love and care.\n     9→\n    10→INGREDIENTS:\n    11→\n    12→3 eggs\n    13→2 cups flour\n    14→2 teaspoons baking powder\n    15→3 cloves garlic\n    16→1 pound beef\n    17→½ cup butter\n    18→2 tablespoons olive oil\n    19→\n    20→INSTRUCTIONS:\n    21→\n    22→1. Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).\n    23→2. Mix dry ingredients in a large bowl.\n    24→3. In another bowl, combine wet ingredients.\n    25→4. Fold dry ingredients into wet mixture.\n    26→5. Pour into prepared pan.\n    27→6. Bake for 25-30 minutes until golden.\n    28→7. Cool before serving.\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a0bd2458-e6bc-4fcb-9e45-2dd61b6b2106","uuid":"65c59735-c948-4215-94d9-e39189d9960f","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Beet Salad.generated.18.txt","content":"SEZON: WIOSNA\n\nBeet Salad\n\nThis dish represents the very best of home cooking traditions. Serve warm to fully appreciate its complex flavors.\nTradycyjny sposób przygotowania, który gwarantuje doskonały smak i doskonałą teksturę.\nOriginating from ancient culinary traditions, this preparation method ensures maximum flavor extraction and nutritional retention.\nThis classic dish brings warmth and comfort to any table. Perfect for family gatherings, it's been passed down through generations with love and care.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n\n3 eggs\n2 cups flour\n2 teaspoons baking powder\n3 cloves garlic\n1 pound beef\n½ cup butter\n2 tablespoons olive oil\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n\n1. Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).\n2. Mix dry ingredients in a large bowl.\n3. In another bowl, combine wet ingredients.\n4. Fold dry ingredients into wet mixture.\n5. Pour into prepared pan.\n6. Bake for 25-30 minutes until golden.\n7. Cool before serving.","numLines":28,"startLine":1,"totalLines":28}}}
