{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018KopvKF9yXVZPAxkEJmCmT","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→Lamb\n     2→Stew\n     3→\n     4→A traditional recipe that celebrates the finest seasonal ingredients. The combination of flavors creates a harmonious blend that delights the palate.\n     5→Tradycyjny sposób przygotowania, który gwarantuje doskonały smak i doskonałą teksturę.\n     6→A beloved family recipe that has stood the test of time. Prepare with patience and attention to detail for best results.\n     7→This dish represents the very best of home cooking traditions. Serve warm to fully appreciate its complex flavors.\n     8→This classic dish brings warmth and comfort to any table. Perfect for family gatherings, it's been passed down through generations with love and care.\n     9→\n    10→INGREDIENTS:\n    11→\n    12→2 cups flour\n    13→2 teaspoons baking powder\n    14→2 tablespoons olive oil\n    15→Salt and pepper to taste\n    16→¾ cup milk\n    17→2 onions, diced\n    18→2 cups vegetables\n    19→\n    20→INSTRUCTIONS:\n    21→\n    22→1. Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).\n    23→2. Mix dry ingredients in a large bowl.\n    24→3. In another bowl, combine wet ingredients.\n    25→4. Fold dry ingredients into wet mixture.\n    26→5. Pour into prepared pan.\n    27→6. Bake for 25-30 minutes until golden.\n    28→7. Cool before serving.\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a0bd2458-e6bc-4fcb-9e45-2dd61b6b2106","uuid":"6cec06d6-3d5d-48ff-9651-ba3bdbf7cd7c","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Lamb Stew.generated.18.txt","content":"Lamb\nStew\n\nA traditional recipe that celebrates the finest seasonal ingredients. The combination of flavors creates a harmonious blend that delights the palate.\nTradycyjny sposób przygotowania, który gwarantuje doskonały smak i doskonałą teksturę.\nA beloved family recipe that has stood the test of time. Prepare with patience and attention to detail for best results.\nThis dish represents the very best of home cooking traditions. Serve warm to fully appreciate its complex flavors.\nThis classic dish brings warmth and comfort to any table. Perfect for family gatherings, it's been passed down through generations with love and care.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n\n2 cups flour\n2 teaspoons baking powder\n2 tablespoons olive oil\nSalt and pepper to taste\n¾ cup milk\n2 onions, diced\n2 cups vegetables\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n\n1. Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).\n2. Mix dry ingredients in a large bowl.\n3. In another bowl, combine wet ingredients.\n4. Fold dry ingredients into wet mixture.\n5. Pour into prepared pan.\n6. Bake for 25-30 minutes until golden.\n7. Cool before serving.","numLines":28,"startLine":1,"totalLines":28}}}
